item.title: CVE-2019-12266|2024-09-17T00:20:34.793Z -- wyze -- cam%20pan%20v2
item.description: Stack-based Buffer Overflow vulnerability in Wyze Cam Pan v2, Cam v2, Cam v3 allows an attacker to run arbitrary code on the affected device. This issue affects: Wyze Cam Pan v2 versions prior to 4.49.1.47. Wyze Cam v2 versions prior to 4.9.8.1002. Wyze Cam v3 versions prior to 4.36.8.32.
